main event: An observer reported sighting a blue object with green lights in Columbus, Ohio during February 1969.
interesting points: The object was about the size of a car,The object was seen moving from west to east on February 4, 1969,It was observed again on February 9, 1969, moving from east to west, There were many high altitude airliners in the area during both sightings, The conclusion from the Air Force was insufficient data for evaluation.
sighted object: a blue object with green colored lights
witness description: the observer reported the sighting in a handwritten letter
